00:30:15.000 --> 00:30:15.640
Haimeng.

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:18.720
Regardez dehors.

00:30:34.000 --> 00:30:34.760
Voulez-vous...

00:30:34.760 --> 00:30:35.420
